100 Dreams

 

100 Dreams is an NFT and a metaverse exhibition of the Swedish artist Kristoffer Kullengren that selects his most representative artworks between 2016 and 2021. Firstly launched in China, the exhibition takes audience through a journey of his best creative state: between dream and reality. 100 Dreams as the NFT is a collective artworks of 100 artworks that symbolize whatâ€™s between dream and reality.
